# HotelOS AI — Engineering Standard Gate

## Status

The binding specification lives in `docs/engineering-standard/00-INDEX.md`.

**Version 1.0 is Approved (2026-07-17).** Application code may be written.

## Golden Rule

Every line of code must meet **100%** of the Engineering Standard. Non-compliant code must not be merged.

## When implementing

Follow volumes 0–13 (+ 5A), especially:

- Positioning: AI Intelligence Layer first (connectors before rip-and-replace)
- TypeScript strict — no `any`
- Clean Architecture / Repository / DI
- AI only via AI Gateway; Memory types separated; Human Approval for autonomous acts
- Tenancy: Platform → Tenant → Chain → Hotel → Department → User
- WCAG 2.2 AA for UI
- PR gate: typecheck, lint, tests, security, secrets, a11y, perf budget

Prefer reading the relevant volume before making changes in that domain.
